  "description": "SPACE macro at 0.75 pre-baked — phaser and prism feedback already deep when the preset loads. Triangle wave with slow attack and long release. Notes dissolve into a prismatic cloud that lingers after key-release. The prism LFO slowly rotates the spectral color of the dissolving fragments. Pure Aether: presence without weight.",
